{"tid":1029673,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"救一首日文歌歌詞翻譯","createTime":"2019-02-20T11:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T09:08:47.000Z","uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc19627a94827703e466d76deeae544eb7e1e434","tid":1029673,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:44:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zpATGf-1tA0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzpATGf-1tA0&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=b4513fc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zpATGf-1tA0</a><br />\n<br />\n悲しいときはいつも<br />\n<br />\n作詞：Goro Matsui<br />\n作曲：Hiroyuki Matsuda<br />\n<br />\n悲しいときはいつも<br />\n蒼い夜空を見上げてた<br />\n君がくれた優しい想い出<br />\n星になるまで<br />\n<br />\nいまは遠い何処か<br />\nなにを忘れてきたのか<br />\n季節ごとの風の名前でも<br />\n思い出せれば&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nこんな涙のあとには<br />\nどんな夢に眠るのだろう<br />\n君の微笑みばかりが<br />\nあればいいのに<br />\n<br />\n海が見える丘で<br />\n摘んだ花の色だけが<br />\n胸に夏を知らせにくるよ<br />\n忘れないで<br />\nもっと沢山の歌詞は ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=f7065036\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a><br />\n<br />\nどんな涙のあとにも<br />\nやがて虹がかならず架かる<br />\nいつか君が眠る場所<br />\n届くようにと<br />\n<br />\nいつまでも　いつまでも<br />\n消えないまま　瞳に揺れる<br />\n好きだった　あの微笑み<br />\n僕は失くしたくない<br />\n<br />\nどこまでも　どこまでも<br />\n終わりのない　空につつまれて<br />\n君と見た　淡い夜明け<br />\n僕は忘れたくない<br />\n<br />\nいつまでも　いつまでも<br />\n消えないまま　心に響く<br />\n少年の　胸の音を<br />\n僕は失くしたくない"},{"pid":"25de2dadbe1baa438dfac9a37eb8cebcb10c7c1d","tid":1029673,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:45:14.000Z","msg":"求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94601e984d5942ef2d9aaf91b8a247965253a221","tid":1029673,"uid":85427,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"悲傷<br />\n望到夜空<br />\n條友有個優異既想發出左黎<br />\n有粒星<br />\n<br />\n遠到唔知邊<br />\n唔記得左咩<br />\n有風既季節係咩名<br />\n諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n喊<br />\n訓著發夢<br />\n淫笑<br />\n啊啊啊啊啊<br />\n<br />\n海上面見到個丘<br />\n摘左朵花有顏色<br />\n夏天係最多胸部睇<br />\n又唔記得左<br />\n<br />\n又喊<br />\n見到彩虹<br />\n上人張床<br />\n呀呀呀呀<br />\n<br />\nbilibala bilibala<br />\n最終乜都係空白<br />\n又睇夜空<br />\n再一次忘記左野<br />\n<br />\nhahaahahaha<br />\n個心消失左但係到響緊<br />\n少年個波仲會發聲<br />\n我又失去野"},{"pid":"6fce5bd5511ee9b2cb2da33049012d7fdd1c6b02","tid":1029673,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94601e984d5942ef2d9aaf91b8a247965253a221","tid":1029673,"uid":85427,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"悲傷<br />\n望到夜空<br />\n條友有個優異既想發出左黎<br />\n有粒星<br />\n<br />\n遠到唔知邊<br />\n唔記得左咩<br />\n有風既季節係咩名<br />\n諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n喊<br />\n訓著發夢<br />\n淫笑<br />\n啊啊啊啊啊<br />\n<br />\n海上面見到個丘<br />\n摘左朵花有顏色<br />\n夏天係最多胸部睇<br />\n又唔記得左<br />\n<br />\n又喊<br />\n見到彩虹<br />\n上人張床<br />\n呀呀呀呀<br />\n<br />\nbilibala bilibala<br />\n最終乜都係空白<br />\n又睇夜空<br />\n再一次忘記左野<br />\n<br />\nhahaahahaha<br />\n個心消失左但係到響緊<br />\n少年個波仲會發聲<br />\n我又失去野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:39:14.000Z","msg":"幾有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a05ebda9e222eeac28a6ae08da29af2522d3d5","tid":1029673,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c947e4db50578166e46b3e3aad38c5f89d012047","tid":1029673,"uid":24457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"もっと沢山の歌詞は ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=f7065036\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a><br />\n呢句翻譯係更多更詳盡歌詞在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=f7065